window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Another Day, Another Gold Piece, Another Unit Destroyed</p> <p>Matt's encountered his first opponent and is getting a hang of being lord of all he surveys. Of course, that's only a few hexes away from his fort, but it's the thought that counts. Now that he has an objective, he's going to need ramp up unit production, balance gold production and the egos of his two Heroes.</p> <p>Just another day when your Magic Kingdom is at War.</p> <p>Magic Kingdom at War is a tactical, base-building, crunchy LitRPG novella series by Tao Wong, bestselling author of the System Apocalypse, A Thousand Li, Climbing the Ranks, the Hidden Universe and Adventures on Brad series.</p>"; 
